layers.nm: Veganism is becoming more popular by the day. Its great to see more people choosing this lifestyle. If youre a new vegan, it can be kind of confusing what you should eat.  Maybe you dont want to commit to a complete vegan diet. Maybe you want to try it out for a bit or need new ideas of possible meals to make. Here are 17 recipes that can be made in 30 minutes or less with simple ingredients you can find at any grocery store.

layers.nm: Vegan diets are on the rise. Many people have made the switch, either temporarily or permanently, from animal products to a plant-based diet for ethical or health reasons. You might be one of those people who want to start a vegan diet and dont know where to start. Most recipes require hard-to-find ingredients or make you buy more ingredients than you actually need. I designed this resource to help new vegans find fast, easy and affordable vegan recipes they can cook in 30 minutes or less. This way you have something delicious to eat in little time without spending your money on expensive ingredients or hard-to-find products.

layers.nm: There are so many reasons to eat vegan that you already know about. Theres the animal rights aspect, the environmental concern, the health aspect (so many vegan recipes are gluten-free), but the most enticing is the fact that vegan food is just plain delicious. But when it comes to getting started you might not know where to begin. Follow our blog to find out how to get started!
